---
title: Rosemary Fig Bavette Steak with Kale & Sweet Potato Jumble
description: Fig jam, cooked down with rosemary and butter, makes a rich, sweet sauce that perfectly complements juicy, seared-then-roasted pork filet. Pair that with earthy roasted sweet potatoes, red onion, and sautéed kale for a hearty and colorful plate; a perfect dinner idea for a night in.

*The serving of protein food in this product is high in protein.*

